'''Knowledge Demon''' is a {{2|Bosses|Boss}} found in {{2|Hive}}.

== Pattern ==
{{Intents|Knowledge Demon|2}}
Knowledge Demon repeats a fixed four-move cycle:
# {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Curse of Knowledge||2}}
# {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Slap||2}}
# {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Knowledge Overwhelming||2}}
# {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Ponder||2}}

After the third {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Curse of Knowledge||2}} (once all three status sets have been offered), the cycle changes: {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Curse of Knowledge||2}} is skipped, and the remaining three moves repeat in order.

== Notes ==
* {{Int|Knowledge Demon|Curse of Knowledge||2}} status sets:
** Set 1: {{BD|Disintegration||2}} (6 damage/turn) or {{BD|Mind Rot||2}} (draw 1 fewer card/turn)
** Set 2: {{BD|Disintegration||2}} (7 damage/turn) or {{BD|Sloth||2}} (max 3 cards/turn)
** Set 3: {{BD|Disintegration||2}} (8 damage/turn) or {{BD|Waste Away||2}} (1 less {{KW|Energy||2}}/turn)

